title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Sign on the outside of a Seattle bar: “Waitress wanted. 25-cent hot dogs every other weekend.” [Submitted by Steve Roth, also of Seattle, who wouldn't work for those wages either.]
